{"tid":1442333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有用文宣】宜家差過沙士？林鄭同藍絲炒晒車！","createTime":"2019-08-11T02:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T14:05:20.000Z","uid":35215,"like":256,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"7e3dc385078dc8456df951e5d0adc216a8d22119","tid":1442333,"uid":35215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:31:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">嗱，我諗呢啲算係有用文宣喇？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭話經濟下行較SARS嚴峻，到底實情係點？去圖啦唔講咁多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQKamhK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQKamhK.jpg&h=f4f18a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於幅圖尋晚做起個draft嘅時候其實已經廣傳，好開心有人好多人睇到幅文宣圖，但由於連續由下午三點做到凌晨四點太眼瞓遲咗出post，希望大家喺facebook都可以幫手share下去D「建制」群組！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=377714286479884&amp;id=352670545650925\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D377714286479884%26id%3D352670545650925&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbUx%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=a95a88e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=377714286479884&amp;id=352670545650925</a>"},{"pid":"8fbd0689336aa662f45b8e16429c5ff511fbb49d","tid":1442333,"uid":3127,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:34:02.000Z","msg":"讓數據來說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2695a66eef2f728761f31e83324ca8d95b1abb14","tid":1442333,"uid":75959,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"