s=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664027dbaa20feb88d987a556386fe8a820718bd","tid":1442333,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"有什麼是抗爭者可做，但還未做的事？X先生說：「第一，我講多次，就係日日打721呢個死穴，因為林鄭同警方依家完全冇得拆。第二，將民建聯同黑警綑綁，要佢哋永不分離。中央撐警，建制派一定要歸隊，冇可能割席。好多人冇留意到北京撐警，其實係一把雙刃劍，好處係穩定軍心，防止警察叛變，壞處係會累死建制派。大家點解唔日日問吓民建聯啲區議員同立法會議員，『你撐唔撐警』、『覺唔覺得警察濫用暴力』呢？記住問是非題，一係yes，一係no，咪畀位佢遊花園呀。」<br />\n<br />\nBy 政界猛人揭林鄭底牌 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e642cf3b7d85f09617edd61f351f85cd8b64c2ed","tid":1442333,"uid":261445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a793c0b0b8597c129d89dee4def8fe11c24c595","tid":1442333,"uid":35215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:55:44.000Z","msg":"屌，唔係咁都推唔起呀？<br />\n葉國謙啲鳩圖就半個鐘上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6081ffeb13c346a2a282445387278101f4f431","tid":1442333,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:56:11.000Z","msg":"勿忘721<br />\n徹查葉虎案"},{"pid":"e21e0c7e95ff264dbb3bf39cb64c2041b9ac7b67","tid":1442333,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:57:31.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"8eb2c7e847e756e7748c060ce6bd7bc596af34d4","tid":1442333,"uid":281467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:57:57.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"a434f5612ab027f5865e93c3ff4ffa6b6e7586f9","tid":1442333,"uid":35215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:03:51.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff52cfe380fa6b52db213e77a48e5733926a4a1